      "citation": "McClish, D. K., Smith, W. R., Levenson, J. L., Aisiku, I. P., Roberts, J. D., Roseff, S. D., & Bovbjerg, V. E. (2017). Comorbidity, pain, utilization, and psychosocial outcomes in older versus younger sickle cell adults: The PiSCES project. BioMed Research International, 2017, 4070547. [PhenX: https://www.phenxtoolkit.org/protocols/view/860601]",
